column5: I was wondering if anyone knows any good camping/fishing spots up north in/around Algonquin area?   Thanks so much!   Andrea
Do you want to relax and enjoy,or are you looking to fish? Arrowhead Park is very nice,and a buddy just spent a week at Bonnie Lake.Said he had a great time.
Are you looking to do a canoe route or just camp... cedar lake near brent is my favorite spot... good lakers and I caught my PB pickeral there as well.
